### Happy path — Turku
POST http://localhost:8080/process
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Teemu",
  "city": "Turku"
}

### Happy path — Helsinki
POST http://localhost:8080/process
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Anna",
  "city": "Helsinki"
}

### Unknown city — falls back to Helsinki coordinates with a WARN log
POST http://localhost:8080/process
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Pekka",
  "city": "Atlantis"
}

### Validation — missing city -> 400
POST http://localhost:8080/process
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Teemu"
}

### Validation — empty name -> 400
POST http://localhost:8080/process
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "",
  "city": "Turku"
}

### Register a user (JSONMOCKDB)
POST http://localhost:8080/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Teemu",
  "city": "Turku"
}

### List all registered users
GET http://localhost:8080/users

### OpenAPI spec
GET http://localhost:8080/openapi.json

### Health
GET http://localhost:8080/health

### --- JSONMOCKDB demo flow ---
### 1) Restart the app with JSONMOCKDB=true (locally: JSONMOCKDB=true camel run process.camel.yaml)
### 2) Try /process for an unregistered user -> 404 with hint
POST http://localhost:8080/process
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Ghost",
  "city": "Helsinki"
}

### 3) Register them
POST http://localhost:8080/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Ghost",
  "city": "Helsinki"
}

### 4) Same /process now succeeds
POST http://localhost:8080/process
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Ghost",
  "city": "Helsinki"
}
